test_quantile <- PI_ALL %>% 
  group_by(FY) %>% 
  mutate(quantile = ntile(SUM_PERCENT_RECEIVED, 5))

test_quantile$quantile <- as.numeric(as.character(test_quantile$quantile))

test_quantile %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = quantile, y = SUM_PERCENT_RECEIVED, colour = FY)) + geom_jitter(alpha = 0.05, width = 0.1, size = 3) + geom_smooth(method = "lm", size = 1.5) + scale_colour_brewer(palette = "Set1") + ylim(0, 0.06)
